{"tid":2427453,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《造星II》季軍李祉均演藝事業無進展 羨慕又妒忌同屆出線兄弟","createTime":"2021-02-28T20:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T09:34:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b7507a22f6723aa9b82c1c6e1ef70b37b9c6e9b5","tid":2427453,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T20:59:04.000Z","msg":"曾獲選為《全民造星II》季軍的李祉均 （Oscar），今晚與《造星III》的李靜蓮（Alina）、黎蘊芝（Dilys）、海淦清（T.Max）、林明燊（Sting）及金汶霏（Ann Kim）在西環出席音樂網上直播。談到《造星II》冠軍吳啟洋（Phoebus）及亞軍張天賦（MC），已分別加盟環球和華納，反而Oscar的演藝事業一直未見起色，Oscar直言很羨慕：「我戥佢哋開心，我諗唔只羨慕，真心嘅，見到佢哋出道好戥佢哋開心，但當我臨瞓前，夜闌人靜嘅時候，點都會有少少妒忌，點解佢哋咁叻，而我又未追到佢哋呢？不過瞓醒覺就覺得唔緊要啦，我再努力啲囉！」他指自己在唱歌及跳舞方面仍需要磨練。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210228/LFFAAGEZ4VAINHPSV2UQ536WJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210228%2FLFFAAGEZ4VAINHPSV2UQ536WJU%2F&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3bZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=7b2091e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210228%2FLFFAAGEZ4VAINHPSV2UQ536WJU%2F&h=34a36243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210228/LFFAAGEZ4VAINHPSV2UQ536WJU/</a>"},{"pid":"eb063ececb2b446c38271db20c6ae6ca15cd4748","tid":2427453,"uid":325346,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T21:06:09.000Z","msg":"Pixel一出道就俾人笑7<br />\n有乜好羨慕？<br />\n可以做既係自己開拓觀眾源<br />\n坤哥之所以做到歌手除左扮棋就係開live同講無聊野"},{"pid":"9adc8d8ab7996eec951e889897c669c663998289","tid":2427453,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T00:25:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3b4604b6c64adeca61748dbe740c8203caba6f0a","tid":2427453,"uid":149833,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:11:20.000Z","msg":"Oscar係藝術型，同另外兩個唔同路線<br />\n相信佢觀眾緣點都好過免費巴<br />\n幫造星III排嘅嘢好睇吖，仲一睇就知係佢嘅style<br />\nOscar BB唔好咁妄自菲薄啦"},{"pid":"5bf4412df66123e35420fa44df425f5de9364bb4","tid":2427453,"uid":13